{"tid":1166161,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唉，朋友撬左人牆腳，話唔話比元配知好？","createTime":"2019-05-22T09:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T03:33:09.000Z","uid":34773,"like":38,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ecf1ead5c98c538e7ad43af21d81bcab389e2951","tid":1166161,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"個fd 睇中條女叫我幫手溝，做左兩個月軍師，<br />\n由搭爹食飯出街我一手鋪排，溝到十分順利。<br />\n上星期係條街/戲院打晒車輪，床都準備上。<br />\n<br />\n星期一發現原來收埋個男朋友（唔識），佢仲日日ot , 一兩個見一次咁大把，我估賺錢準備結婚因為都3x歲唔細。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條女諗緊點分手，同我fd 一齊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下如果我女朋友偷情真係會好sad, 成世有陰影。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />親手間接溝人條女，又親手送佢落地獄會唔會好賤。應該點做好。唔通拆散番朋友佢地？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps:條女乖乖女外表中間唔算靚，估唔到都咁賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打真係要睇實d 自己條女，唔好成日ot 唔陪佢。"},{"pid":"7a56aeb5f3c5dcc21f364925619abe62b75f91c7","tid":1166161,"uid":126690,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:24:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73c691f7ccfdae88b0062b8f4c40ebbf2c6d001b","tid":1166161,"uid":9726,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:25:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3551da2cafc9492c6f8b8b66a8f41c30b307c2d","tid":1166161,"uid":253954,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:27:36.000Z","msg":"帽唔怕帶最緊要除得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371323fec53f6bdf72ce28c9ad29211346745107","tid":1166161,"uid":241106,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:29:24.000Z","msg":"萬一其實你個朋友根本唔想知呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b13cbe05140a7beee0b9f9ad3a3e398d5b49138","tid":1166161,"uid":102514,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:32:06.000